targets.query: SELECT max("queued_load") FROM (SELECT mean("queue") / mean("running") AS "queued_load" FROM (SELECT mean("pendingTasks") AS "queue", mean("running") AS "running" FROM /^tc_queue2/ WHERE $timeFilter AND "provisionerId" = 'releng-hardware' GROUP BY time($__interval), "provisionerId", "workerType", "workerGroup" fill(previous)) GROUP BY time($__interval), "provisionerId", "workerType", "workerGroup")  GROUP BY time($__interval), "provisionerId", "workerType", "workerGroup"

SELECT mean("pendingTasks") AS "queue", mean("running") AS "running" FROM /^tc_queue2/ WHERE $timeFilter AND ("provisionerId" = 'gecko-t' AND "workerType" = 't-linux-xlarge') OR ("provisionerId" = 'gecko-3' AND "workerType" = 't-linux-xlarge') GROUP BY time($__interval), "provisionerId", "workerType", "workerGroup" fill(previous)
SELECT min("pendingTasks") / min("running") FROM "tc_queue2_exec" WHERE ("workerType" = 'gecko-3-b-osx-1015') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "workerType", time($__interval) fill(linear)
SELECT min("workers") FROM "tc_queue2_exec" WHERE ("workerType" = 'gecko-3-b-osx-1015') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "workerType", time($__interval) fill(linear)
